===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr|en}} {{m|fr|accommodation}} from {{etyl|la|en}} {{m|la|accommodātiō||adjustment, accommodation, compliance}}, from {{m|la|accommodō||adapt, put in order}}. Superficially {{suffix|accommodate|ion|lang=en}}. The sense of "lodging" was first attested in 1600.

